# QuickQuack Game

A fun board game for coworkers where players move their characters based on real-life sales achievements. Players can roll dice to move forward on the board and collect prizes from special tiles.

## Features (Planned)
- User authentication for coworkers
- Character selection
- Interactive board game
- Dice rolling mechanics
- Prize tiles
- Sales achievement tracking

## Tech Stack
- Next.js
- TypeScript
- Vercel for deployment
- Tailwind CSS for styling

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
3. Run the development server:
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```
4. Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) in your browser

## Development
This project is built with Next.js and TypeScript, providing a modern and type-safe development experience.